cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category as it proposes a new deep reinforcement learning algorithm that learns representations to accelerate learning from images. It also uses high-capacity deep networks and a critic model to learn within a compact latent space. 

It is also likely to belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category as it deals with learning policies for complex control tasks directly from high-dimensional image inputs. 

The cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category is also likely as the paper deals with learning from image observations. 

The cs.RO (Robotics) sub-category is another possibility as the paper deals with learning policies for control tasks. 

Finally, the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper deals with learning policies for control tasks and uses a critic model.
